### Blog API Testing Examples
### Make sure to replace localhost:3000 with your actual server URL
### Replace JWT tokens with actual tokens received from login/register

### 1. Register a new user
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "username": "johndoe",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Login user
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Get user profile (protected)
GET http://localhost:3000/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 4. Get all users
GET http://localhost:3000/users

### 5. Get user by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/users/USER_ID_HERE

### 6. Update user profile (protected - own profile only)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/users/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "johnupdated"
}

### 7. Get all published blogs
GET http://localhost:3000/blogs

### 8. Create a new blog (protected)
POST http://localhost:3000/blogs
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First Blog Post",
  "content": "This is the content of my first blog post. It contains some interesting information about web development.",
  "description": "A blog post about web development",
  "isPublished": true
}

### 9. Get blog by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/blogs/BLOG_ID_HERE

### 10. Get blogs by author (protected)
GET http://localhost:3000/blogs/author/AUTHOR_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 11. Update blog (protected - author only)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/blogs/BLOG_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Blog Title",
  "content": "This is the updated content of my blog post.",
  "isPublished": false
}

### 12. Delete blog (protected - author only)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/blogs/BLOG_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 13. Delete user (protected - own profile only)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/users/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE